    <item>
      <title>对特朗普的痴迷给民主带来了代价</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/17/us/politics/trump-elections-politics.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统要求采取措施解决投票的公正性问题，他坚持对自己 2020 年选举的失败进行重新诉讼，同时想方设法对 2026 年的选举结果提出质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/17/us/politics/trump-elections-politics.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 09:06:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着巴黎附近大火蔓延，极端高温正在改变法国的灭火方式</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/17/france-forest-fires-extreme-heat.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[直到最近，法国的森林火灾主要发生在南部。本周，大火在更北的地方肆虐。法国不得不重新考虑其消防策略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/17/france-forest-fires-extreme-heat.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 09:01:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
